dc_description_s: This data represents streambank easements for Dane County, Wisconsin in 2020. [Streambank Easements typically extend 33 feet from the stream bank and allow public fishing and hiking along the corridor. Access is also allowed for ongoing management and maintenance purposes. --This data layer is included in the DCiMap application and the Land and Water Resources Viewer. ]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For the most recent version of this data, please visit: https://gis-countyofdane.opendata.arcgis.com/.
